{"tid":418962,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母海乜撚野歸啊","createTime":"2017-09-30T05:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T11:32:57.000Z","uid":18245,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"35ca58d510488bce1c44e7e193c9db619839a470","tid":418962,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:00:13.000Z","msg":"竟然可以無人屌 <br />\n<br />\n海歸特指從海外留學歸國的人員，在<span style=\"color: red;\">支那</span>頗為流行。因為「海歸」和「海龜」諧音，因此也有作「海龜」的用法。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n有浸過鹹水唔用 用埋曬啲垃圾支那字 <br />\n唔出聲屌果啲都係仆街黎 <br />\n就係無人出聲 選擇左沉默<br />\n先會搞到今時今日咁 <br />\n求下你班人唔好再用埋啲支那字啦屌"},{"pid":"f08f442111f75a273f1fe6a1b3549f15c499dbe0","tid":418962,"uid":150611,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd3ab9959af26c1ebe60cc4fb172ffddeeb75c97","tid":418962,"uid":3773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T05:19:21.000Z","msg":"浸過鹹水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02d1e902d5c43495d6b94868a31dc2f7813b29c","tid":418962,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T10:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc593264fffbfa173eed823d480cc7a5420526b","tid":418962,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:43:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40733ef6f1c177c716efd8180f5a3d10fd39a220","tid":418962,"uid":5588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:44:02.000Z","msg":"海歸係大陸潮語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/